name: Speed Nation Vinyl Sticker
description:
High quality, die cut vinyl sticker. Suitable for outdoor application.

Perfect size for windscreens, quarter windows, skateboards or your bosses office door.

Available in either two tone Red/White and also White Only.

Dimensions: 18cm x 6cm.

name: Premium Casual Tee. GT-R R33 Godzilla.
description:
Mighty Godzilla! The king of Japanese Performance!

Designed to be worn in any casual situation. Our high quality premium tee's use the latest in printing technology that transforms you into a walking piece of art without ever having to worry about your shirt fading, flaking or cracking.

Our shirts are thick, soft, quick drying and more importantly very comfortable to wear. They look and feel like cotton, but are made of a ring-spun high performance polyester. Our fabric features built-in superior moisture management, temperature control, anti-bacterial and anti-odour properties; it regulates body temperatures and keeps the skin dry, acting as a base layer, even during extreme conditions.

*Small and Medium SOLD OUT.
